Women everywhere deserve access to a full spectrum of birth control options. Unfortunately, that isn’t always the reality. If you live in an area where a specific method isn’t available and you are using the “Method Chooser” tool with women, you can deselect each method not available in your area so it won’t be suggested as a possible choice. If things change and a method later becomes available, you can reselect it as an option. Deselecting a method here only removes it from the results in the “Method Chooser.”
